        "text": "held in 1 hand",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
      }
    },
    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This brass censer dangles on a length of chain. Most *thuribles of revelation* are adorned with swirling Empyrean text, though some are iron and feature Diabolic or Chthonian text.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
